《迷你地铁》是一款[[益智游戏|解谜]][[策略游戏|策略]]游戏，玩家需要为发展迅速的城市搭建高效的[[鐵路運輸|铁路]][[地鐵|运输网络]]<ref name="gamestm_review">{{cite web | url=http://www.gamestm.co.uk/reviews/mini-metro-review/ | title=Mini Metro review | work=GamesTM | publisher=Imagine Publishing | date=2016-02-15 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160619071531/http://www.gamestm.co.uk/reviews/mini-metro-review/ | archive-date=2016-06-19 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

截至2022年2月，可选地图包括：[[倫敦地鐵|倫敦地鐵]]、[[巴黎地鐵|巴黎地鐵]]、[[紐約地鐵|紐約地鐵]]、[[芝加哥地鐵|芝加哥地鐵]]、[[柏林地鐵|柏林地鐵]]、[[墨爾本地鐵|墨爾本地鐵]]、[[港鐵|香港港鐵]]、[[巴塞罗那地鐵|巴塞罗那地鐵]]、[[大阪地鐵|大阪地鐵]]、[[斯德哥尔摩地鐵|斯德哥尔摩地鐵]]、[[聖彼得堡地鐵|聖彼得堡地鐵]]、[[蒙特婁地鐵|蒙特婁地鐵]]、[[三藩市地鐵|三藩市地鐵]]、[[聖保羅地鐵|聖保羅地鐵]]、[[首爾地鐵|首爾地鐵]]、[[聖地亞哥地鐵|聖地亞哥地鐵]]、[[华盛顿地鐵|华盛顿地鐵]]、[[新加坡地鐵|新加坡地鐵]]、[[開羅地鐵|開羅地鐵]]、[[伊斯坦堡地鐵|伊斯坦堡地鐵]]、[[上海地鐵|上海地鐵]]、[[廣州地鐵|廣州地鐵]]、[[重慶地鐵|重慶地鐵]]、[[南京地铁|南京地铁]]、[[孟买地鐵|孟买地鐵]]、[[拉各斯地鐵|拉各斯地鐵]]、奧克蘭地鐵、[[亞的斯亞貝巴輕軌|亞的斯亞貝巴輕軌]]。

每张地图都以平面形式展现现实中的城市。每关开局有三个车站<ref name="indiegames_nov_9">{{cite web | url=http://indiegames.com/2015/11/mini_metro.html | title=Relax and make your own Mini Metro | work=IndieGames.com | publisher=UBM | first=Lena | last=LeRay | date=2015-11-09 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212212308/http://indiegames.com/2015/11/mini_metro.html | archive-date=2015-12-12 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="killscreen_review">{{cite web | url=https://killscreen.com/articles/mini-metro-makes-mass-transportation-sublime/ | title=Mini Metro makes mass transportation sublime | work=Kill Screen | publisher=Kill Screen | first=Ethan | last=Gach | date=2015-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709111055/https://killscreen.com/articles/mini-metro-makes-mass-transportation-sublime/ | archive-date=2016-07-09 | dead-url=yes | access-date=2016-07-09 }}</ref>，后期会有形状各异的车站出现。玩家需要用直线串连车站，构筑铁路路线，每条路线用不同的颜色代表<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" /><ref name="rps_aug_2014">{{cite news | url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/08/26/mini-metro-early-access-review/ | title=Impressions: Mini Metro | newspaper=Rock, Paper, Shotgun | publisher=Rock, Paper, Shotgun | first=Alec | last=Meer | date=2014-08-26 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410154411/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/08/26/mini-metro-early-access-review/ | archive-date=2016-04-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。出现在车站的每个乘客有不同的形状，这些形状代表着他们打算前往的车站<ref name="rps_aug_2014" />。河流、交汇的地铁线路、越来越多的车站和乘客会让铁路系统的管理越来越复杂<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" /><ref>{{cite web | url=https://killscreen.com/articles/mini-metro-turns-headache-mass-transportation-fun/ | title=Mini Metro turns the headache of mass transportation into fun | work=Kill Screen | publisher=Kill Screen | first=Emanuel | last=Maiberg | date=2014-08-18 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709104824/https://killscreen.com/articles/mini-metro-turns-headache-mass-transportation-fun/ | archive-date=2016-07-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。普通形状的车站在后期会转变为罕见形状<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" />。游戏画风奉行[[极简主义|极简主义]]，采用直线和鲜艳颜色，复刻现代铁路[[路线图|路线图]]<ref>{{cite web | url=https://killscreen.com/articles/learn-science-subway-mini-metro/ | title=Learn the science of the subway in Mini Metro | work=Kill Screen | publisher=Kill Screen | date=2015-11-12 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220084329/https://killscreen.com/articles/learn-science-subway-mini-metro/ | archive-date=2016-02-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在“普通模式”（Normal Mode）下，每个车站乘客吞吐量均有限，站内拥挤到一定阈值则游戏结束<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" />，但之后玩家可以选择在“无尽模式”中继续构筑铁路网，此时车站吞吐量不设限<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" />。游戏中每一周结束，玩家会获得升级道具，舒缓由铁路网扩张所加剧的运输压力，包括新增列车、新增线路、新增铁路隧道、新增车厢或是新增[[换乘站|换乘枢纽]]（吞吐量较一般车站更大，可缩短乘客上下车等待时间），但所有道具只有一个。玩家可以随时暂停列车运行，以便重建或调整路线<ref name="rps_aug_2014" />，但“极限模式”（Extreme Mode）下，路线一旦设置便不可更改<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" /><ref name="gamezebo_review">{{cite web | url=http://www.gamezebo.com/2016/10/20/mini-metro-review-mass-transit-brain-teaser/ | title=Mini Metro Review: Mass Transit Brain Teaser | work=Gamezebo | publisher=Gamezebo | first=Rob | last=Rich | date=2016-10-20 | access-date=2016-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025002958/http://www.gamezebo.com/2016/10/20/mini-metro-review-mass-transit-brain-teaser/ | archive-date=2016-10-25 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年，游戏新增“创意模式”（Creative Mode），以网格状显示地图，提供无上限的车站、列车、车厢、隧道或换乘枢纽，供玩家自由设计铁路网络<ref>{{cite web |title=Creative mode |url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/287980/view/2891830130672191187 |website=Steam News |accessdate=2021-05-22 |date=2018-11-20 |archive-date=2021-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713044351/https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/287980/view/2891830130672191187 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

