根据汇总媒体[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]，游戏获得评论人“普遍好评”<ref name="metacritic_pc" /><ref name="metacritic_ios" />。《科技说》（''Technology Tell''）作者珍妮·拉达（Jenni Lada）认为游戏虽然有意令玩家感到压力，但画风“赏心悦目”，玩起来非常惬意<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.technologytell.com/gaming/136613/mini-metro-preview-stress-free-subway/ | title=Mini Metro Preview: Stress-free subway | work=Technology Tell | publisher=GadgeTell | first=Jenni | last=Lada | date=2014-10-13 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709121527/http://www.technologytell.com/gaming/136613/mini-metro-preview-stress-free-subway/ | archive-date=2016-07-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Gamasutra|IndieGames.com]]的莉娜·莱瑞（Lena LeRay）认为游戏让人非常放松，称赞界面直观<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" />，又对团队在抢先发行阶段所做的变更表示赞赏，认为音频和“每日挑战”（Daily Challenge）这两项新增内容备受欢迎，界面改良令她最初的抱怨情绪得以平息<ref name="indiegames_nov_9" />。《[[GamesTM|GamesTM]]》评测PC版时，认为玩法所蕴含的深度及难度设定让该作徒增趣味<ref name="gamestm_review" />，但对游戏未在[[智能手机|智能手机]]端发行表示不解，理由是游戏界面简约界面而非常适合这类平台<ref name="gamestm_review" />。《{{tsl|en|Kill Screen|Kill Screen}}》编辑伊森·加奇（Ethan Gach）称赞游戏简约、典雅，将交互美学与强大模拟系统相结合<ref name="rps_aug_2014" />。他尤为欣赏难度逐渐增加，游戏体验以优雅姿态过渡到混乱之中，“就算是灾难也很典雅”，又认为作品为抢先发行的游戏树立了典范<ref name="rps_aug_2014" />。《[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo]]》作者罗伯·里奇（Rob Rich）评价手机版时，对其视觉设计表达赞赏，又指出触控手段直观。他指出，以几何图形表示通勤者及车站能够将任务化繁为简，令该作通俗易懂<ref name="gamezebo_review" />。《[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]]》评论克里斯蒂安·瓦伦丁（Chrisitan Valentin）认为游戏在早期引人疑惑，但最终“意外地引人入胜”<ref name="pocket gamer review" />。

游戏在2016年[[独立游戏节|独立游戏节]]上获得“优秀音频奖”（Excellence in Audio）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2016-03-17-her-story-dominates-gdc-igf-awards | title=Her Story dominates GDC, IGF Awards | work=Gamesindustry.biz | publisher=Gamer Network | first=James | last=Brightman | date=2016-03-17 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421061350/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2016-03-17-her-story-dominates-gdc-igf-awards | archive-date=2016-04-21 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，另获提名“优秀视觉艺术”（Excellence in Visual Art）、“优秀设计”（Excellence in Design）及“[[谢默斯·麦克纳利大奖|谢默斯·麦克纳利大奖]]”三项提名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/263099/2016_Independent_Games_Festival_debuts_finalists.php | title=2016 Independent Games Festival debuts finalists | work=Gamasutra | publisher=UBM plc | date=2016-01-06 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405072749/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/263099/2016_Independent_Games_Festival_debuts_finalists.php | archive-date=2016-04-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>；获{{tsl|en|12th British Academy Games Awards|第12届英国游戏学院奖}}“最佳游戏处女作”（Debut Game）提名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/267721/Everybodys_Gone_to_the_Rapture_leads_BAFTA_nominations.php | title=Everybody's Gone to the Rapture leads BAFTA nominations | work=Gamasutra | publisher=UBM plc | first=Chris | last=Kerr | date=2016-03-10 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404140626/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/267721/Everybodys_Gone_to_the_Rapture_leads_BAFTA_nominations.php | archive-date=2016-04-04 | dead-url=no }}</ref>；获第16届[[游戏开发者选择奖|游戏开发者选择奖]]“最佳游戏处女作”（Debut Game）提名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamechoiceawards.com/winners/index.html | title=16th Annual Game Developers Choice Awards | work=Game Developers Choice Awards | publisher=UBM plc | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401004641/http://www.gamechoiceawards.com/winners/